(222, 1, '2012-09-01 09:57:29', '2012-09-01 09:57:29', 'Ideas can change the world.Â People make ideas happen. We believe the genius within people creates ideas and that ideas incite the genius within people. Weâ€™ve worked with international organizations, media, and government to bring ideas to life. We do this by creating an environment within your organisation that allows ideas to flow. In doing so, we match Innovation withÂ Innervation â€“ the unique insights and emotions that an individual draws upon to create cool stuff and solve complex problems. We find that sweet spot where chaos and order meet â€“ and where ideationÂ begins.', 'Ideas to Life', 'We work with social, business and public sectors to co-create ideas that possess the charisma and the vision to be memorable, effective and practical...', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '112-revision-12', '', '', '2012-09-01 09:57:29', '2012-09-01 09:57:29', '', 112, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/standby/112-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2, 1, '2012-08-11 06:10:21', '2012-08-11 13:10:21', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://geniusworks.co.za/standby/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2012-08-11 06:10:21', '2012-08-11 13:10:21', '', 0, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/standby/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
