(290, 1, '2012-09-20 19:32:31', '2012-09-20 19:32:31', 'We run workshops that enable individuals and teams to see with new eyes; bringing awareness to unlock their creativity and uncover uncommon insights.\r\n\r\nYou and your co-workers will learn skills that can meet a changing world. You will learn to nurture radical collaborations, run innovation boot-camps and to facilitate idea laboratories. We will train you to think like a Genius.', 'Training', 'We teach individuals and organizations the core skills needed to deal with ambiguity, create opportunity and lead with Imagination.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '96-revision-9', '', '', '2012-09-20 19:32:31', '2012-09-20 19:32:31', '', 96, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/standby/96-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2012-09-20 19:24:57', '2012-09-20 19:24:57', 'We all need co-pilots to help us uncover new pathways of thought, deal with blind spots, remember what we learned in the rear view mirror and reveal what is possible on the road ahead.\r\n\r\nGenius works offers one-on-one coaching and mentoring sessions which are focused on exploring your needs from a most basic to a more specialized level. We have a rich and diverse array of experience to shape your coaching session into the unique support system that fits who you are.\r\n\r\nWe in-sight, challenge, inspire and provoke deep reflection and imagination within our coaching sessions. We motivate and assist you to improve your bottom-line effectiveness and harvest more rewarding careers, more meaningful personal and family lives and a more connected relationship to yourself. We mentor you to uncover, recover and discover your Genius and bring new insights and foresights to help you become the best of who you uniquely and truly are. In our mentorship roles we honor the age old tradition that has been lost to many; the passing on of knowledge and wisdom.', 'Coaching and Mentoring', 'We incite, challenge and inspire you into your brilliance.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-revision-19', '', '', '2012-09-20 19:24:57', '2012-09-20 19:24:57', '', 92, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/standby/92-revision-19/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
