(198, 1, '2013-04-17 16:39:13', '2013-04-17 16:39:13', 'Our forte is in understanding the core underlying needs in an organisation and its people. To excavate the golden questions we run processes and do assessments before getting everyone into one space to cook. Often organisations will pump resources into finding solutions before they have even understood the question.\n\nWe take people into the challenging places they must go in order to find gold.\n\nOnce we are in the room, we act as a catalyst for people to think about and to voice what is really going on at various levels and we use this as the impetus for solution making. We hold an approach that everything has levels of complexity and therefore all pieces play a vital role. We get you out of the habit of thinking reductively and into the practice of thinking expansively and inclusively, to create wholeness within the organisation.\n\nUsing a model of strategy, humanity and co-design we highlight questions around desirability, possibility and viability.', 'Facilitating strategy and group dynamics', 'Genius lies in the conversation. We work with teams to unravel knots and uncover key strategies.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '98-autosave', '', '', '2013-04-17 16:39:13', '2013-04-17 16:39:13', '', 98, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/standby/98-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
