(381, 1, '2013-01-28 09:59:09', '2013-01-28 09:59:09', 'We are a group of passionate individuals who live for understanding how genius solutions can (and have) change the world. We don''t mince words, we share, inspire and assist you to access your own brilliance. We have travelled the world learning the latest modalities and approaches that are required for a complex world and we are here to serve you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900;">Oran Cohen</span></strong>\r\n\r\nOran loves peopleâ€¦and also, the things that they create. He has dedicated his work to facilitating otherâ€™s genius in solving complex and difficult problems in various contexts. He continuously aims to understand the subtleties of the business world and the art of creating true and lasting change within its walls.Founder of Genius Works Consulting.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900;">Claire Janisch</span></strong>\r\n\r\nClaire is a sustainability &amp; innovation advisor and biomimicry professional. She is a graduate of and a co-trainer for the international 2-year biomimicry Professionals Program (BPCP). She currently heads up biomimicrySA. Claire works in the areas of strategy, technology &amp; education.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900;">Riaan Fourie</span></strong>\r\n\r\nRiaan is a consumer-centric Brandscaper, with a passion for inclusive, community orientated creative marketing strategies. With a strong focus on social media, multimedia and events, Riaan transforms brands into resonating stories. Driven by the goal to engage, awaken and enable others, he uses a dynamic interplay of strategy and communication to inspire.\r\n\r\nAt Genius Works he meaningfully solves problems for others, exploring and establishing multi-dimensional solutions.', 'The Genius Team', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-01-28 09:59:09', '2013-01-28 09:59:09', '', 34, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/34-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(382, 1, '2013-01-28 10:02:30', '2013-01-28 10:02:30', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b></b><b>Oran Cohen Â | Â Managing Director Â | Â Head Facilitator</b>\r\n\r\nOran has dedicated his work to facilitating othersâ€™ genius in solving complex problems in various contexts. As aÂ facilitator and entrepreneur, Oran has over 12 yearsÂ experienceÂ in facilitating people and their ideas in more than 20 countries. As a serial innovator, Oran has imagineered documentaries, international leadership programmes as well as founded Non-Profit Organisations.\r\n\r\nOran is a SETA accredited facilitator and assessor. He has studied various forms of facilitation and methods such as Creative Problem Solving with Disneyâ€™s Imagineers and is currently completing his masters in Leading Innovation and Change through York St John University.\r\n\r\nIn 2009 he was selected as one of the most interesting young South Africans by theÂ <i>Mail and Guardian</i>Â and has been called an emerging young global leader. In 2011 he was chosen as one of 50 International Evolutionary Leaders by the Source of Synergy Foundation.\r\n\r\nOran has worked and consulted in both private and public sectors and collaborated on specific projects with municipalities and a wide range of organisations. In these organisations he facilitated product innovation and ideation, leadership training, strategy, and creative thinking.\r\n\r\nOran is the Managing Director and founder of Genius Works Consulting.', 'Oran Cohen', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'oran-cohen', '', '', '2013-09-11 13:27:57', '2013-09-11 13:27:57', '', 0, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/?page_id=382', 0, 'page', '', 0),
