(390, 1, '2013-04-17 17:16:11', '2013-04-17 17:16:11', '<script type="mce-text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\n\n\n  var _gaq = _gaq || [];\n  _gaq.push([''_setAccount'', ''UA-38011189-1'']);\n  _gaq.push([''_trackPageview'']);\n\n  (function() {\n    var ga = document.createElement(''script''); ga.type = ''text/javascript''; ga.async = true;\n    ga.src = (''https:'' == document.location.protocol ? ''https://ssl'' : ''http://www'') + ''.google-analytics.com/ga.js'';\n    var s = document.getElementsByTagName(''script'')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);\n  })();\n\n// ]]></script>\n\nWe are a group of passionate individuals who live for understanding how genius solutions can (and have) change the world. We don''t mince words, we share, inspire and assist you to access your own brilliance. We have travelled the world learning the latest modalities and approaches that are required for a complex world and we are here to serve you.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900;">Oran Cohen</span></strong>\n\nOran loves peopleâ€¦and also, the things that they create. He has dedicated his work to facilitating otherâ€™s genius in solving complex and difficult problems in various contexts. He continuously aims to understand the subtleties of a changingÂ world and the art of creating true and lasting change within it. Oran is known as the executive imagineer and is the Managing Director of Genius Works Consulting.\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a title="Oran Cohen" href="http://geniusworks.co.za/oran-cohen/">Read More</a></span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span style="color: #ff9900;">Claire Janisch</span></strong>\n\nClaire is a sustainability &amp; innovation advisor and biomimicry professional. She is a graduate of and a co-trainer for the international 2-year biomimicry Professionals Program (BPCP). She currently heads up biomimicrySA. Claire works in the areas of strategy, technology &amp; education.\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a title="Clai