(544, 1, '2013-01-28 11:43:45', '2013-01-28 11:43:45', '<script type="text/javascript">\r\n\r\n  var _gaq = _gaq || [];\r\n  _gaq.push([''_setAccount'', ''UA-38011189-1'']);\r\n  _gaq.push([''_trackPageview'']);\r\n\r\n  (function() {\r\n    var ga = document.createElement(''script''); ga.type = ''text/javascript''; ga.async = true;\r\n    ga.src = (''https:'' == document.location.protocol ? ''https://ssl'' : ''http://www'') + ''.google-analytics.com/ga.js'';\r\n    var s = document.getElementsByTagName(''script'')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);\r\n  })();\r\n\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nKnown as an Imagineer, Oran has the ability to facilitate ideas into reality and has served as an inspiration in innovation and creative strategy to individuals and organizations all over the world. Oran is a passionate business and social entrepreneur, consultant, facilitator, musician, designer and creative strategist.\r\n\r\nIn 2009 Oran was selected as one of the most interesting young South Africans by the Mail and Guardian and has been called an emerging young global leader. In 2011 he was chosen as 1 of 50 International Evolutionary Leaders by the Source of Synergy Foundation Non-Profit, â€œEvolutionary Leadersâ€. make link - <a href="http://www.evolutionaryleaders.net/">www.evolutionaryleaders.net</a>\r\n\r\nOran has worked and consulted in both private and public sectors and collaborated on specific projects with municipalities and organizations such as Cadbury, Johnson &amp; Johnson (America &amp; Ireland), Standard Bank, Cape Union Mart, Sappi Saicor, Deloitte, the Netherlands Embassy,Â  SABC, Talent Attack, and Raizcorp. In these organisations he facilitated product innovation and ideation, leadership training, strategy, leadership communication skills and creative thinking.\r\n\r\nHe is a SETA accredited Facilitator and Assessor. He also trained with Disneyâ€™s Imagineering team in Florida, USA. He has run workshops and interventions in Asia, America, Canada, Africa and Europe. Oran has spoken at the United Nations in 2003 during the International Day of Peace and is now a board member on a United Nations NGO called â€œChildren of the Earthâ€.\r\n\r\nOran is the Managing Director and founder of Genius Works Consulting.', 'Oran Cohen', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '382-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-01-28 11:43:45', '2013-01-28 11:43:45', '', 382, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/382-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
