/h3>\r\n<span style="font-size: 14px;">Often when we try to create change or innovation, we expend a lot of energy on taking action in a system without understanding the underlying structures at play. This module brings together Biomimicry and Systems Thinking to understand how to design smarter and more enduring solutions to the problems we face.</span>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.5em;">Module 4: Leading and Shaping the Story\r\n</span><i>Traditional and Digital Storytelling for Change-Makers.</i></h3>\r\n<span style="font-size: 14px;">Everything is a story; systems, organisations, products, relationships. This module equips participants with the basics of how to lead and shape stories in order to mobilise, lead, transform and empower people and brands.</span>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.5em;">Module 5: Enrolling the Tribe\r\n</span><i>Creating Ideas that Stick and Building a Following for Change.</i></h3>\r\n<span style="font-size: 14px;">Enrolling the tribe is about moving from â€œsalespersonâ€ to â€œpartnerâ€. Itâ€™s about the art of enrolling others into your ideas, creating buy-in for new initiatives and co-creating visions in teams, organisations, with stakeholders and communities.</span>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.5em;">Module 6: Navigating the Unknown\r\n</span><i>Leadership Tools to Deal with Ambiguity and Change.</i></h3>\r\n<span style="font-size: 14px;">In a constantly changing world, flexibility, spontaneity and accelerated decision making are skills that are becoming indispensible. Navigating the Unknown unpacks the challenges and the approaches to navigating the dancing landscapes we face.</span>', 'Our Flagship Offering', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '448-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-01 16:36:56', '2015-10-01 16:36:56', '', 448, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/448-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
