(932, 4, '2016-03-17 09:18:39', '2016-03-17 09:18:39', '<blockquote><a href="http://geniusworks.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/download-1.png" rel="attachment wp-att-973"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-973" src="http://geniusworks.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/download-1.png" alt="download (1)" width="300" height="168" /></a>\r\n\r\n'' Design is a behaviour not a department'' - David Milne</blockquote>\r\nNo longer just a tool for product designers, design thinking is being applied as a powerful methodology for thinking through complex challenges and creating novel ideas and possibilities.\r\n\r\nDo you need to design a product, a service, an organisation or a solution? In design anything you will learn how to bring cutting edge Design Thinking into your own environment, This complex problem solving methodology taps into people''s unexpressed needs and desires to create effective, often ground-breaking solutions that delight stakeholders and customers.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://geniusworks.co.za/design-anything-outcomes/">http://geniusworks.co.za/design-anything-outcomes/</a>', 'Design Anything', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'design-anything', '', '', '2016-03-24 13:21:34', '2016-03-24 13:21:34', '', 0, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/?post_type=sfwd-courses&#038;p=932', 0, 'sfwd-courses', '', 0),
