(934, 4, '2016-03-17 09:19:08', '2016-03-17 09:19:08', '<blockquote>'' Fail often so you can succeed sooner.'' - Tom Kelley, IDEO</blockquote>\r\nPrototype anything is a fun, messy and interactive dive into the process of prototyping your ideas and potential solutions. This experiential and practical programme offers delegates a trip into the mindset and the methods of designing testable prototypes of products, services,interactions and or/social initiatives.\r\n\r\nPrototype allows you to experiment, receive feedback, fail fast and learn even faster! Expect to roll your sleeves up as you plan and build prototypes. prototype anything gives you a push into the realm of practicing and experiencing real life iterations of your ideas, and brings the promise of innovation to life.\r\n\r\nOutcomes:\r\n\r\nIn prototype <strong>anythingÂ </strong>participants will...\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Learn creative, low-cost ways to prototype and test the underlying assumptions of your solutions.</li>\r\n	<li>Prototype ideas across diverse fields and areas ( products, services, structures, software, social interactions, designs).</li>\r\n	<li>Discover and practice the core principles and behaviour shifts required for safe-to-fail experimentation with far reaching benefits in your work and life.</li>\r\n	<li>Engage more deeply with users, customers and stakeholders, gaining valuable feedback from tangible rapid prototyping.</li>\r\n	<li>Learn to give and receive feedback on a regular basis in different environments; whilst building an experimental, learning mind-set.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'Prototype Anything', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prototype-anything', '', '', '2016-03-22 10:47:55', '2016-03-22 10:47:55', '', 0, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/?post_type=sfwd-courses&#038;p=934', 0, 'sfwd-courses', '', 0),
(935, 4, '2016-03-17 09:19:08', '2016-03-17 09:19:08', '', 'Prototype Anything', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '934-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-17 09:19:08', '2016-03-17 09:19:08', '', 934, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/934-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(936, 4, '2016-03-17 09:21:06', '2016-03-17 09:21:06', '<blockquote>''In every job that must be done there is an element of fun.'' - Mary Poppins</blockquote>\r\nGamification isn''t simply about playing games. It''s about applying game-based thinking to your brand, business or organisation. Because it is so effective, gamification has emerged as one of the most popular new organisational tools in business, education, the non-profit sector and government. It enables individuals and groups to learn faster, solve problems together and achieve unimaginable goals.\r\n\r\nBy understanding and applying the basics of game mechanics you will be able to change how people engage with your projects and enhance the value of their input dramatically. Gamification can be applied to a diverse range of challenges and applications.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://geniusworks.co.za/gamify-anything-outcomes-2/">http://geniusworks.co.za/gamify-anything-outcomes-2/</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Gamify Anything', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gamify-anything', '', '', '2016-03-24 14:21:55', '2016-03-24 14:21:55', '', 0, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/?post_type=sfwd-courses&#038;p=936', 0, 'sfwd-courses', '', 0);
