(979, 4, '2016-03-22 09:11:08', '2016-03-22 09:11:08', '<blockquote>''In every job that must be done there is an element of fun.'' - Mary Poppins</blockquote>\nGamification isn''t simply about playing games. It''s about applying game-based thinking to your brand, business or organisation. Because it is so effective, gamification has emerged as one of the most popular new organisational tools in business, education, the non-profit sector and government. It enables individuals and groups to learn faster, solve problems together and achieve unimaginable goals.\n\nBy understanding and applying the basics of game mechanics you will be able to change how people engage with your projects and enhance the value of their input dramatically. Gamification can be applied to a diverse range of challenges and applications.\n\nOutcomes:\n\nIn gamify <strong>anything</strong> participants will...\n<ol>\n	<li>Understand and apply the basics of game mechanics and change how people engage with their products.</li>\n	<li>Use creative, serious play as a ''game -changer'' for your organisation.</li>\n	<li>Understand when to apply gamification and when not to.</li>\n	<li>Apply the core principles of gamification to different types of situations.</li>\n	<li>Design a game intervention, applying the tools to a real life scenario.</li>\n	<li>Learn how people''s behaviour can be positively changed through gamifiation and feedback.</li>\n	<li>Move beyond '' carrot-and-stick'' rewards to deeper behavioyral motivation strategies</li>\n</ol>', 'Gamify Anything', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '936-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-22 09:11:08', '2016-03-22 09:11:08', '', 936, 'http://geniusworks.co.za/936-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
